  coords 3380.589 24.415 3529.858
  m_sTitle "Mission Notes"
  m_sTextData "Blue AO Limit is for the platoon."\
  "Green AO Limit is for the OP so they can conduct forward reconnaissance."\
  ""\
  "Note: Once a member of the OP team crosses back into the Blue AO Limit, they can no longer go back outside of it. "\
  ""\
  "OP team spawns a different location and has no radio, they have a third person so they can send a runner back to Platoon if they need to but they are meant to retreat into the Blue AO limit once they have information to pass on."
